Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:40.10,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,All the pirates vying for the One Piece\Nhead for the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:42.68,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,People call it the "New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:51.42,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the only one to ever conquer\Nthese waters was the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:57.73,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:04.08,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Now, the boy whose body turned to rubber\Nafter eating the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:07.37,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nventure into that very sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:11.50,Default,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,After surviving a fierce battle on Fishman Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the Straw Hats reach the New World at long last—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the harshest sea, ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,After receiving an emergency signal,\Nthey landed on Punk Hazard,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,a strange island divided into two parts—\Nthe Burning Lands and the Frozen Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?! It's like a thin film...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.11,0:03:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Everybody, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do a roll call!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,--Chopper! --Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,--Franky! --Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Nami... aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You stupid pirate, don't push your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You ate the Op-Op Fruit and you're the modification man, I believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of his sword's reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are in my way! Get out of the circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The circle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,While you're in the circle he created,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you're like a patient on an operating table!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is his operating room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:05:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He has total control over it and can manipulate anything as he pleases!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the Surgeon of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Tashigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Haki is not strong enough!
