Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Captain-chan got cut in half!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hey, you're alive, aren't you?! --Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How dishonorable! I got sliced but I'm still breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just kill me, Trafalgar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk like a master swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you something, Navy soldier girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The weak can't even pick their way to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't reach me with that sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can chop you more if you liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you! Stop insulting our Captain-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain-chan, don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll riddle that fool with bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullets?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How did the bullets get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did the bullets that we shot go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the bullets you shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I switched them with the snow falling over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he invincible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down! He's gonna cut everything again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can stop his sword attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard! Captain-chan, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Smo-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Surgeon of Death--Trafalgar Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop messing with the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel an unpleasant energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You have Sea Prism Stone on the tip of your jitte, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! The recoil made the sword cut the artwork!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.13,0:09:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship's gonna fall onto us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's run! He doesn't want us to be here anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you're a Warlord or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Admiral Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain-chan, let's get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,--But... --He's no match for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,White Blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Get out of the circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-They were strong... Too strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat Luffy and his crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! They took Boss Brownbeard with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We got to help the Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They're cold-blooded pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.27,0:10:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what they're gonna do to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss Brownbeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to let the Master know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me, those of you who can stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:58.11,Sign,,0,0,366,,{\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\fs60\bord2.2\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}Team Luffy, Frozen Lands
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.44,0:10:58.11,Sign,,0,0,366,,{\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\fs60\bord0\4a&HFF&}Team Luffy, Frozen Lands
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a huge noise. Was it Sanji and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Alliga-taur!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't know what happened to my crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I won't tell you anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Then run faster! To the building that Brook saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta save Nami and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How humiliating to lose to such a squirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You robbed my people so cruelly of all they had, you cheap muggers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to give us a bad name!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys attacked us first!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're showing no sign of remorse, alligator guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Brook, I know you don't feel cold because you don't have flesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So why did you steal the coat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I felt like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to see you all again so I wanted to share in your feeling cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad that Nami and the others were abducted in those clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope they don't get frostbite and lose their limbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, Robin! Don't share those gruesome concerns!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Law and Smoker are in a big battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the plan was just to make them go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But those escaped pirates took the kids in the Biscuits Room with them
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and ran into Law and the others at the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Navy saw the children?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I feared the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they know something is going on on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we kill Smoker,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the Navy will become aware that something is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You just got back - what are you doing now, Monet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.46,0:13:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It was them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We should have paid better attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I forgot to mention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk's dragon and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Brownbeard's Centaur Patrol Unit have been defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,--What?! --Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means those pirates you kidnapped along with
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,their ship had other crew members
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and they were in the Burning Lands already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They made it across the lake and they'll be here in a matter of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They were so strong. Now look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:44.44,"Sign",,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}"The Straw Hats Are Back"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it was them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you have heard about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They're an unforgivable archenemy not just for the Navy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but for the World Government too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:13:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The World Government, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're so notorious, maybe it's good for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's the Straw Hats or Smoker,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,we can get rid of all those troublemakers who are learning what's
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,going on on this island at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But Master, even if they're a group of misfits,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,if we kill all the G-5 soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.76,0:14:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the Navy would be on the alert, wouldn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can just suppress things that are going to
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.64,0:14:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,happen on the island from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,--Call Joker. --Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:02.42,Sign,,0,0,363,,{\blur0.3\fad(1040,0)\fs60\bord2.2\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(995,1040,\1a&H00&)}Team Sanji\NA mountain behind the {research }institute
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.42,0:15:02.42,Sign,,0,0,363,,{\blur0.3\fad(1040,0)\fs60\bord0\4a&HFF&}Team Sanji\NA mountain behind the {research }institute
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it out from the backdoor but what should we do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with this strange transformation going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,we have to keep running for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?! It's super confusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,--Bros! --W-We're gonna freeze to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Deadly cold? I don't give a damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The samurai and the brats? I don't give a damn anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there a camera somewhere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna take a picture before we return to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you gonna take a picture of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.05,0:15:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And stop having nosebleeds in my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is more important, Nami! Don't button up my aloha shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's cold but hang on a little bit longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Spiral Bro is being kind! It's too creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? Did you get your bodies switched?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being treated very differently from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.11,0:16:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know humans felt this cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Bros, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it... I-I can't even move...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,--Me too! --I'm freezing too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! We shouldn't have taken them with us when
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,we didn't know where to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel cold at all with this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Pieces of the ship are falling like leaves off a tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Smo-yan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain-chan, how is your body? Did they stick together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, your right hand is my left foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My hands! Whose feet are these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! We're in big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost our means of communication and the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the Warlords were on our side! That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey, Captain-chan, don't try to move! Stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tashigi, keep this in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates will always be pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates will be pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No one, not even pirates or Government allies,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is allowed to be here on this island, Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you people are not allowed, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Law, why are you here on Punk Hazard?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I never understood why you joined the Warlords in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What we need to do now is to achieve higher status.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates all over the world have started to pay respect
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Straw Hats because of the incident at Enies Lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put all my pride on the line and kick their asses in the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's the Straw Hats...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...or the Warlord who serves for the World Government - Trafalgar Law,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,pirates will be pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never trusted you Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.20,0:20:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:21:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's behind this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you up to on this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you answer first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you all up to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.96,0:21:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There are things that you can't see unless you change your standing, Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Scalpel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.22,0:22:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.42,0:22:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to tell you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.64,0:23:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoker collapses after his heart is stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,With Law looking down coldly before them,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.73,0:23:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the rage of Tashigi and the G-5 reaches its peak and they attempt an attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.67,0:23:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When Luffy suddenly appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.61,0:23:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The meeting between the two, who share a deep bond from the great war,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.97,0:23:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,causes the situation to drastically change!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.67,0:23:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.97,0:23:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Reunited After Two Years!\NLuffy and Law"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.41,0:23:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
